race.description: 'Raising Hope With Stephâ€™ Bragger Cup Handicap (Bm50)
race.comment: Tricky race. DREAM INHERIT (2) was narrowly beaten at big odds last start over 1400m at Cootamundra. Expect Ramsbotham to go forward again and inject her into the race. Could take catching if she turns up on song. DANISH HUSSAR (10) led and proved too strong at Narromine, making it two straight. Faces a tougher test but deserves respect. MEMPHIS TENNESSEE (8) improved second-up at Canberra and will be better again stepping to the mile on the quick back-up. Represents value. KERMA ART (9) doesn't win often but has peaks that stack up. McDougall's booking is a strong push. STAR EMPIRE (7) finds it hard to land the knockout blow but is holding form and can be competitive again.
